  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db4\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc4\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd4 \u0d91\u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Our aerial work is also shown abroad",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Air Force says that the head of the peacekeeping force, Mr. Lt. Gen. Daniel Sidki Traore, has appreciated the active contribution of the Sri Lanka Air Force helicopter squadron on duty in the Central African Republic to successfully prevent an attack by the armed forces of the Central African Republic by a rebel group operating there. .",
        "The Air Force says that the Sri Lankan Air Force helicopter squadron launched a successful attack by using two helicopters to support the ground operations troops and that the attack defeated the rebels and the power in the area came to the hands of the African Republic Army.",
        "According to the announcement issued by Air Force Media Director Group Captain Dushan Wijesinghe, the Sri Lanka Air Force has provided about 100 million US dollars to the country by deploying troops to UN peacekeeping duties."
      ],
